<para>
  When &oof2; is <link
  linkend="Section-Concepts-Mesh-Solving">solving</link> a time
  dependent problem, all <link linkend="Chapter-Graphics">Graphics
  Windows</link> will be updated when
  <classname>GraphicsUpdate</classname> is <link
  linkend="Section-Tasks-ScheduledOutput">scheduled</link>.  If
  <classname>GraphicsUpdate</classname> is not scheduled, the window
  will not be updated until the time evolution is complete.
</para>
<para>
  Only the &layers; that have their <varname>when</varname> parameter
  set to <link
  linkend="Object-Placeholder-Time"><userinput>latest</userinput></link>
  will be redrawn when the window is updated.
</para>

